# {{projectName}}

API automation framework built with Supertest, Jest, and TypeScript.

## Overview

This is a production-ready API testing framework using Supertest for HTTP assertions, Jest as the test runner, and TypeScript for type safety. Perfect for testing REST APIs with comprehensive validation and reporting.

## Features

- ✅ Supertest for API testing with built-in assertions
- ✅ TypeScript for type safety and better IDE support
- ✅ Jest test runner with HTML reporting
- ✅ JSON Schema validation
- ✅ Environment-based configuration
- ✅ Comprehensive logging with Winston
{{#if cicdTool}}
- ✅ CI/CD ready with {{cicdTool}}
{{/if}}
- ✅ Data-driven testing support

## Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+ and npm

## Installation

```bash
npm install
```

## Configuration

Update `config/environments.ts` with your API endpoints:

```typescript
export const environments = {
  qa: {
    baseUrl: 'https://api-qa.example.com',
    timeout: 30000
  },
  prod: {
    baseUrl: 'https://api.example.com',
    timeout: 30000
  }
};
```

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
npm test

# Run smoke tests
npm run test:smoke

# Run with coverage
npm run test:coverage

# Watch mode
npm run test:watch
```

